43:24.302 --> 43:27.038
And this
is how revolutions start --

43:27.072 --> 43:31.242
not with a big bang
but with a small victory.

43:32.744 --> 43:36.247
And it might take years
of hard-fought activism,

43:36.281 --> 43:39.718
